additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Sodium Bicarbonate, Potassium Caroate, Sodium Carbonate, Sodium Carbonate Peroxide, Sodium Sulfate, Malic Acid, PEG-150, Citric Acid, Sodium Dodecylbenzenesulfonate, PEG-90, Aroma, TAED, CI 28440, CI 42090.

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep out of reach of children, and elderly in need of care. For soaking dentures only. Do not place tablets in mouth. Do not drink the solution. Harmful is swallowed. Avoid contact with eyes. Causes serious eye irritation. Causes skin irritation. Wash hands thoroughly after handling. For advice, contact a Poisons Information Centre (Phone Australia 13 11 26; New Zealand 0800 764 766) or a doctor. If swallowed: Call a poison centre or doctor if you feel unwell. If medical advice is needed, have product container or label at hand. If in eyes: rinse cautiously with water for several minutes.
